title: Week 8 recap
itunes:title: Week 8 recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler, Dan Hanzus and Colleen Wolfe – break down each game from Week 8 of the regular season, including a shootout in New Orleans between the Giants and the Saints, and a dominant Broncos team knocking off the Packers from the ranks of the undefeated.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
